Macros

macro toToml(obj: untyped): TomlValueRef
Converts the given object into a PrefsNode if possible
  • Arrays are converted into sequences
  • {key: val, ..} are converted to ordered tables.

Example:

let data = toToml({
  "num": 10,
  floating: 10.23,
  users: @["a", 1, false],
  names: [],
  keybindings: {:},
  scheme: {
    background: "#000000",
    font: "UbuntuMono"
  }
})
Source   Edit
